Jaane bahaaraan rashke chaman

Ghunchah dahan seemeen badan

Ay jaanemann

Jaane baharan rashke chaman

Ghunchah-dahan seemeen-badan

Ay jaane mann jaane bahaaraan

Jannat ki hoorein tujhpe fida

Raftaar jaise mauje saba

Rangeen ada tauba shikan

Ay jaane mann jaane bahaaraan

Jaane baharan rashke chaman

Ghunchah-dahan seemeen-badan

Rangeen-ada tauba-shikan

Jaane baharan o jaaneman

Jaane baharan o jaane mann

Nazron ne teri kiya hai sitam

Qause quzah ki yeh rangeeniyan

Jaadu kiya hai yeh tune sanam

Taubah hai taubah teri ada

Uski inaayat husn tera

Rangeen-jamaal naazuk badan

Gul-pairahan sarwe chaman

Jaane baharan o jaane mann

Shaam-e furozaan aankhen teri

Har ik nazar men jaadu gari

Zulfe teri mushke khutan

Ay jaane mann jaane baharan

Ay naaz-parwar naaz-aafreen

Laakhon haseen hain tujh sa nahi

Khandah-jabeen, sheereen sukhan

Ay jaane-mann, ay jaane mann

Ghunchah-dahan seemeen-badan

Rangeen ada tauba shikan

Har ik nazar mein jaadu gari

Zulfen tiri mushke khutan

Ay naaz-parwar naaz-afreen

Laakhon haseen hain tujh sa naheen

Khandah-jabeen, sheereen sukhan

Ay jaane manne jaane mann
